location.fullValue: Durbin Plan, Pleasanton Meadows : Cottage Collection

data.description: Cozy, very welcoming, 4 bedroom 1 bath home. comes with lots of charm and charisma. This beautiful home sit's central of the city & comes with Laminate flooring in the living room and throughout the house. Home does come with a sprinkler system and a big back yard, great for entertaining and for the kids to play. Lots of shade in both back and front of the yard. a nice spacious shed that can be converted into SHE-shed, mature trees, all schools are minutes away. This home is walking distance to the local grocery store and all the eatery's it provides. don't miss out on this opportunity. schedule the tour today.
